","identifier":"ic_folder_categories.png"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents","title":"Components"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSSuggestionChip":{"kind":"symbol","title":"OUDSSuggestionChip","abstract":[{"text":"Suggestion chip is a UI element that allows to present recommended or predictive options based on user’s input or context,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and is commonly used to capture filtering decisions.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Suggestion chip is typically non-selected by default and can be tapped or clicked to apply the suggestion, streamlining input and enhancing usability.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Chips can show multiple interactive elements together in the same area, such as a list of selectable movie times, or a serie of email contacts.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Best suited for category-based filters that do not require additional visual elements.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudssuggestionchip","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSSuggestionChip","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSuggestionChip","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSSuggestionChip","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/documentation/OUDSThemesContract/OUDSTheme":{"fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSTheme","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"OUDSTheme","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/OUDSTheme","abstract":[{"text":"This is a basic theme any theme must be a subclass off, or all themes must have as ancestor.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A Swift ","type":"text"},{"code":"class","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" has been used so as to allow to easi